Run the following commands one by one:

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:arne-alamut/freenect
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install freenect
sudo adduser YourUserName video
sudo freenect-glview

Now you need to install wrappers for python. Navigate to the directory libfreenect/Wrappers/python and run this code

sudo python setup.py install.

Note: If you get an error like "pyconfig.h" not found, install python-dev by running the following command:

sudo apt-get install python-dev.
